TITLE: Creating an Agent in SpinAI with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a calculator agent using the createAgent function, specifying instructions, available actions, and the LLM model to use for decision making.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fallomai/spinai/blob/main/apps/docs/get-started/introduction.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const calculatorAgent = createAgent({
  instructions: `You are a calculator agent that helps users perform mathematical calculations.`,
  actions: [sum, minus],
  model: openai("gpt-4o"),
});
```

